         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Images from Ashmolean\n\nThese images are copyright for Ashmolean and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEA\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEA', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Fragment of the epic <i>Enmerkar and the lord of Aratta</i>. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite0>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgHarappaW\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgHarappaW', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Harappa Seal. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite1>). Shared under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Cradles of civilization (Parte II) (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>The Writing System (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgS\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgS', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Estatuillas of the Sixth Dynasty. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite2>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>What is the extent of the impact of the flood? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgKL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgKL', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Sumerian King List. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<htcite3>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Cradles of civilization (Part I) (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Sumerian King List (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>What is time? (<a href=\"index.html?page=history\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('history','html', '', false); return false;\">History</a>)</li><li>Fractionating Texts (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>The Writing System (<a href=\"index.html?page=literature\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('literature','html', '', false); return false;\">Understanding Texts</a>)</li><li>Is it possible to live in the sky? Is the Earth flat? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li><li>What is the extent of the impact of the flood? (<a href=\"index.html?page=myths_believes\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('myths_believes','html', '', false); return false;\">Myths and Believes</a>)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
